title: Our iHeartCountry Festival was a BLAST! Amy Met George Strait, TikToker Josh Woods performs with The Raging Idiots, Bobby had to fill-in for an Artist Who Missed A Meet and Greet + We Give Out The Biggest Truck in Country Music Award
itunes:title: Our iHeartCountry Festival was a BLAST! Amy Met George Strait, TikToker Josh Woods performs with The Raging Idiots, Bobby had to fill-in for an Artist Who Missed A Meet and Greet + We Give Out The Biggest Truck in Country Music Award
description:
We recap stories from our iHeartCountry Festival in Austin, TX over the weekend. Bobby talks about George Strait surprising the crowd, Jake Owen having the best performance and Josh Woods from TikTok getting to perform with the Raging Idiots. We awarded the “Biggest Truck In Country Music” award and talked to the winner.
